entries.title: Idaho murders: Moscow police hits out at 'speculation and unvetted information'
entries.description: Moscow, Idaho, police are addressing "unvetted information" circulating in the media, reminding the public to look at police bulletins for updates on the investigation into the murders of four University of Idaho students.

entries.title: Nevada U.S. senator introduces 'abortion funds' bill
entries.description: (The Center Square) – U.S. Sen. Catherine Cortez Masto introduced legislation Thursday that would create a federal grant program for organizations that connect women to reproductive health care and abortion resources, her office announced.
